 Federal Regulations, or any successor regulation; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s7214a/a/3/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s7214a/a/3","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs7214a%2Fa%2F3%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"i","heading":null,"label":"i","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s7214a/a/3/B/i","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s7214a/a/3/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs7214a%2Fa%2F3%2FB%2Fi","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"is the equivalent of, or substantially similar to, the form described in clause (i) or (ii) of subparagraph (A); and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"clause","nativeType":"clause","number":"ii","heading":null,"label":"ii","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s7214a/a/3/B/ii","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s7214a/a/3/B","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs7214a%2Fa%2F3%2FB%2Fii","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"a foreign issuer files with the Commission under the Securities Exchange Act of 1934 ( et seq.) or rules issued under that Act;15 U.S.C. 78a","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":null,"label":"4","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s7214a/a/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s7214a/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs7214a%2Fa%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the terms “covered issuer” and “non-inspection year” have the meanings given the terms in subsection (i)(1) of , as added by section 2 of this Act; andsection 7214 of this title","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"5","heading":null,"label":"5","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s7214a/a/5","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s7214a/a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs7214a%2Fa%2F5","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the term “foreign issuer” has the meaning given the term in section 240.3b–4 of title 17, Code of Federal Regulations, or any successor regulation.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":"Requirement","label":"b Requirement","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s7214a/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s7214a","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs7214a%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s7214a/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s7214a/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs7214a%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"that, during the period covered by the covered form, such a registered public accounting firm has prepared an audit report for the issuer;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"2","heading":null,"label":"2","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s7214a/b/2","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s7214a/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs7214a%2Fb%2F2","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the percentage of the shares of the issuer owned by governmental entities in the foreign jurisdiction in which the issuer is incorporated or otherwise organized;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"3","heading":null,"label":"3","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s7214a/b/3","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s7214a/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs7214a%2Fb%2F3","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"whether governmental entities in the applicable foreign jurisdiction with respect to that registered public accounting firm have a controlling financial interest with respect to the issuer;","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"4","heading":null,"label":"4","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s7214a/b/4","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s7214a/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs7214a%2Fb%2F4","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"A","heading":null,"label":"A","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s7214a/b/4/A","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s7214a/b/4","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs7214a%2Fb%2F4%2FA","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the issuer; or","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subparagraph","nativeType":"subparagraph","number":"B","heading":null,"label":"B","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s7214a/b/4/B","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s7214a/b/4","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs7214a%2Fb%2F4%2FB","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"the operating entity with respect to the issuer; and","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]},{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"5","heading":null,"label":"5","identifier":"/us/usc/t15/s7214a/b/5","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t15/s7214a/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft15%2Fs7214a%2Fb%2F5","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"whether the articles of incorporation of the issuer (or equivalent organizing document) contains any charter of the Chinese Communist Party, including the text of any such charter.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]}]}]}
